# Module qat-devices

This module *qat-devices* is part of [myQLM](https://pypi.org/project/myqlm/) project. myQLM is a quantum
software stack for writing, simulating, optimizing, and executing quantum programs.

This module provides a set of predefined HardwareSpecs objects corresponding to existing or common topologies.

## Prerequisites
This version of myQLM works for Windows (with **Python 3.6**, **Python 3.7** or
**Python 3.8** 64-bit version), for MacOS (with **Python 3.6**, **Python 3.7** or
**Python 3.8** 64-bit version) and for Linux (with **Python 3.6** or
**Python 3.8** 64-bit version).

This module can be installed by typing the following command:

```
pip install myqlm
```
